Source Description:
Here we have Sloth, and wide awake even! She's a red fox by species, but by color she's quite yellow. She's super fast, yet lazy. Though she moves when she absolutely has to. Otherwise you can find her napping at the job.

Speaking of jobs, Sloth here is the quest giver! You can find her in the quest hall laying at her desk giving out quests to all the skilled adventurers.

She might even give Sam special quests that keep him out of trouble. But what fun would that be? These quests may turn out bigger than our fennec fox expects.

I've got the comic behind this series planned out to all of Volume 1 and I'm revising it as I come up with new ideas. I'll be streaming concept work like this image over at  https://picarto.tv/Kuroodod 

Thanks for reading! More on the way! x3

And don't forget to follow me on the new Twitter at https://twitter.com/Kuroodo_D

[section,expanded=Artist's Description]
hitaki318 and I decided to use two roulette wheels to decide a subject and a theme for this challenge.

We got 'Robin Hood' with one wheel, and 'Swap Universe' with the next. That means we had to spin the first wheel again, and see what universe the Robin Hood character would swap with, and got 'El Dorado.'
SO, of course I had to draw Maid Marian in Chel's outfit. I'd like to think they were traveling to El Dorado to ally their two kingdoms, (Or spend their honeymoon there) and Robin Hood convinced Maid Marian that this was the typical garb. XP
